[objects clattering]

47
00:04:51.613 --> 00:04:54.699
-[Pete] Hey, Marcus! Marcus!
-[horse whinnies]


48
00:04:54.783 --> 00:04:57.494
-You wanna go over to our house?
-Hell, no!


49
